HEALTH_DESCRIPTION_64: Khazikani bwino, muyamwitseni mwana wanu ndikukhala ndi ubwenzi ndi wopereka thanzi wanu! Masiku 10 oyamba ndi otetezeka kwambiri. Yang'anirani zizindikirozi kwa inu. Kuwotcha, kugwedera, kapena kutuluka kununkhira kuchokera kumkazi, kugwedera.
HEALTH_DESCRIPTION_65: Mwana wanu: kuwotcha, kugwedera, kuvuta kuyankha, kusayenda, kulephera kuyamwa. Itanani thandizo mwachangu pamene muli ndi vuto lililonse!
ANY_OTHER_QUESTION_1: Fotokozani mavuto ena omwe muli nawo...
THANK_YOU_1: Zikomo Amayi! RHP wanu adzawerenga izi ndikukulankhulani ngati n'kofunika. Ngati zizindikiro zikukwera, itanani wopereka thanzi kapena chipatala choyandikana. Fomu yasinthidwa kuti mugwiritse ntchito mtsogolo.
